videos.description: On fourth-and-two, Horned Frogs WR KaVontae Turpin takes the snap and runs right before throwing across the field to Sewo Olonilua who breaks free for 20 yards and a first down.
videos.headline: TCU converts trick play on 4th down

videos.description: Kyle Hicks take a handoff at the goal line and jumps over the pile to score a 1-yard touchdown, giving the Horned Frogs an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: TCU strikes first as Hicks leaps into end zone

videos.description: On third-and-17, TCU quarterback Kenny Hill uses his legs, rushing for 27 yards and a first down.  The drive would result in a field goal.
videos.headline: TCU's Hill scrambles for long 3rd down conversion

videos.description: Texas converts on fourth-and-three as Shane Buechele finds Chris Warren III along the right sideline for a 12-yard gain, setting up a Longhorns' field goal.
videos.headline: Longhorns move the chains on 4th down

videos.description: Kyle Hicks runs left and follows his blockers, reaching the end zone untouched for a 14-yard score.
videos.headline: Hicks scampers in for Horned Frogs TD

videos.description: Longhorns QB Shane Buechele goes deep, lofting a pass to  Lil'Jordan Humphrey for a 37-yard gain, getting Texas down to the TCU 38-yard line.
videos.headline: Texas airs it out to enter TCU territory

videos.description: Shane Buechele throws to Collin Johnson who makes an acrobatic catch in coverage for a 33-yard Texas score.
videos.headline: Johnson makes contested grab in end zone for Longhorns TD

videos.description: TCU coach Gary Patterson says the Horned Frogs' uptempo offense is the reason they lead at halftime.
videos.headline: Patterson pleased with TCU's first-half performance

videos.description: On third-and-four, Shane Buechele drops back and is brought down in the backfield by Ty Summers for a 12-yard loss forcing a Longhorns punt.
videos.headline: Texas QB sacked on 3rd down

videos.description: On fourth-and-one, Darius Anderson runs for the first down and more, juking a Texas defender and scoring a 31-yard touchdown, giving TCU a 24-7 lead.
videos.headline: Horned Frogs find paydirt with rushing TD on 4th down

videos.description: Shane Buechele evades pressure in the pocket and rolls right before finding Lil'Jordan Humphrey who outruns the defense and gets all the way down to the TCU 35-yard line for a 42-yard gain.
videos.headline: Longhorns break into TCU territory with huge gain

videos.description: TCU head coach Gary Patterson praised his team's performance saying the Horned Frogs executed well enough to win the game.
videos.headline: Patterson: 'We didn't beat ourselves'

videos.description: TCU quarterback Kenny Hill says the team's 24-7 win over Texas was a complete team effort, citing the play of the offensive line and running game as keys to the victory.
videos.headline: Hill: 'Great team win' over Longhorns
